00:44:45.480 --> 00:44:46.120
Shake a leg!

00:44:46.200 --> 00:44:46.760
We are almost late.

00:44:47.600 --> 00:44:48.840
Sometimes, her imagination is so wild

00:44:49.720 --> 00:44:50.920
that I don't know
what comments I should make.

