I'm telling you,

00:45:03.480 --> 00:45:04.080
that's not going to happen!

00:45:07.120 --> 00:45:08.120
The silly things she did...

00:45:08.120 --> 00:45:08.960
Masterpieces of world literature?

00:45:09.000 --> 00:45:10.200
Stop watching it.

00:45:10.800 --> 00:45:11.800
I didn't see the first part clearly.

00:45:11.800 --> 00:45:13.480
Wait a moment.

00:45:13.480 --> 00:45:13.960
Wait!

00:45:14.120 --> 00:45:15.560
My hair gets tangled with the umbrella rib.

00:45:15.560 --> 00:45:17.880
The silly things she did often
made me feel hopeless.

00:45:23.960 --> 00:45:24.480
Let's go.

