She is so interesting.

00:45:51.320 --> 00:45:53.000
I can't help following her.

00:45:58.960 --> 00:46:00.000
When I came round,

00:46:01.520 --> 00:46:02.760
she had dragged me

00:46:02.800 --> 00:46:04.360
out of my quiet

00:46:05.000 --> 00:46:05.680
and cold world.

00:46:05.680 --> 00:46:06.280
Come on in.

00:46:07.280 --> 00:46:07.560
Hmm.

00:46:07.560 --> 00:46:08.200
It's cold outside.

00:46:18.960 --> 00:46:21.080
It seems you can be happy
no matter what happens.

00:46:22.040 --> 00:46:24.160
I began to feel things from her perspective.

00:46:25.160 --> 00:46:27.520
I found that no matter
how serious the matter was,

00:46:28.360 --> 00:46:30.960
she could handle it in a wonderful way.

00:46:33.480 --> 00:46:34.160
It starts now.

00:46:37.880 --> 00:46:38.760
Does it look like fireworks?

00:46:39.120 --> 00:46:41.520
Look at the glorious fireworks
I set off for you.

00:46:44.560 --> 00:46:45.440
Take it.

00:46:45.640 --> 00:46:46.400
Point it at me.

00:46:47.040 --> 00:46:47.640
Press it.

00:46:48.680 --> 00:46:49.160
Have a try.

00:47:04.440 --> 00:47:05.040
Press it again.

00:47:11.160 --> 00:47:12.040
Alright.

00:47:14.560 --> 00:47:15.360
However,

00:47:17.000 --> 00:47:18.280
I am boring and dismal.

00:47:18.280 --> 00:47:19.760
(Bipolar Disorder: Genetic Risk 41.1)

00:47:19.760 --> 00:47:20.360
I am not

00:47:20.360 --> 00:47:21.040
qualified

00:47:22.160 --> 00:47:23.400
to have her.

00:47:29.240 --> 00:47:30.160
We need to break up.

