I thought I would return

00:47:33.200 --> 00:47:35.000
to my quiet and cold world at worst.

00:47:37.200 --> 00:47:38.560
But I didn't expect that

00:47:39.800 --> 00:47:40.800
without her,

00:47:41.640 --> 00:47:43.520
I would be like an island.

