From all directions,

00:47:46.880 --> 00:47:49.240
the biting sea wind poured in while moaning.

00:47:50.680 --> 00:47:52.080
It turned out that my world

00:47:53.440 --> 00:47:55.080
could be emptier

00:47:56.680 --> 00:47:57.880
and colder.

